description: Gut rehab newly renovated unit in City Point, at corner of N St and E 5th in City Point, just take a brief walk to the M St. Beach and you can enjoy the M Street beach. This unit gets lots of sunshine thru the large windows, 12 feet high ceiling with open layout kitchen, hardwood floor throughout the unit, central AC, in-unit laundry, and large storage room in basement. Two bedrooms with bathroom en-suite, including dual closets in main bedroom with ample closet space for all of your wardrobes. One year builder's warranty is included, condo fee is estimated. Conveniently located near Castle Island, Seaport, and the best dining and entertainment experience of Boston are just short distance away. Short distance to Seaport and downtown Boston, Route 93 and 90 highway access within 10 minutes. Come and check out this newly renovated unit today!
